      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ETERNALLY YOURS (2) landed midfield last start at this track and trip and just missed in a photo finish. He rates highly on the back of that effort and lines up here third-up and ready to peak. Tricky draw, but he'll just need to replicate his latest effort to be going one better here. SEA OF GALILEE (1) steps out in trip today after pulling up with an issue here two back. He was solid off a short freshen back in distance last start and he was trending the right way before that issue two back. Back on song now and can make his presence felt. GILDED REIGN (3) was strong here three back and getting up to 1500m is no issue. Looks suitably placed in this assignment and he should get every chance from an inside barrier. BELLE OF BONDI (9) disappointed on debut, but the market expected a much better performance. Can turn it around here without surprising. TASMAN JEWEL (7) can be in the finish come back in distance.",
